37 class OmegaCV : public TransferModel

58 public:
59  OmegaCV(Mutation::Mixture& mix)
60  : TransferModel(mix)
61  {
62  m_ns = mixture().nSpecies();
63  mp_wrk1 = new double [m_ns];
64  mp_wrk2 = new double [m_ns];
65  };
66 
67  ~OmegaCV()
68  {
69  delete [] mp_wrk1;
70  delete [] mp_wrk2;
71  };
78  double source()
79  {
80  static int i_transfer_model = 0;
81  switch (i_transfer_model){
82  case 0:
83  return compute_source_Candler();
84  break;
85  default:
86  std::cerr << "The selected Chemistry-Vibration-Chemistry model is not implemented yet";
87  return 0.0;
88  }
89  }

109 double const OmegaCV::compute_source_Candler()
110 {
111 
112 
113  // Getting Vibrational Energy
114  mixture().speciesHOverRT(NULL, NULL, NULL, mp_wrk1, NULL, NULL);
115 
116  // Getting Production Rate
117  mixture().netProductionRates(mp_wrk2);
118 
119  // Inner Product
120  double c1 = 1.0E0;
121  double sum = 0.E0;
122 
123  for(int i = 0 ; i < m_ns; ++i)
124  sum += mp_wrk1[i]*mp_wrk2[i]/mixture().speciesMw(i);
125 
126  return(c1*sum*mixture().T()*RU);
127  }
